 "last_reply_by": "atan", "last_touched": 1611439493, "title": "非可视距离组网方案", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/747638", "created": 1611375636, "content": "迫于宽带提价，两套房子想共享宽带使用，非可视距离，直线距离大概 260 米左右。\r\n\r\n\r\n之前有尝试过（其他小区）使用水星定向网桥 5.8G 15km 组网，直线距离 500 米，间隔一栋高层，有 30-40M 的带宽。我猜测可能是侧边有建筑，是折射、衍射的信号。\r\n\r\n\r\n现在的情况，中间间隔 4 栋高层，外加两侧没有建筑物可以折射、衍射，可能用不了这款网桥。（暂未测试）\r\n\r\n\r\n是否还有其他解决方案？\r\n\r\n\r\n![]( https://i.v2ex.co/m4K924XC.jpeg)", "content_rendered": "<p>迫于宽带提价，两套房子想共享宽带使用，非可视距离，直线距离大概 260 米左右。</p>\n<p>之前有尝试过（其他小区）使用水星定向网桥 5.8G 15km 组网，直线距离 500 米，间隔一栋高层，有 30-40M 的带宽。我猜测可能是侧边有建筑，是折射、衍射的信号。</p>\n<p>现在的情况，中间间隔 4 栋高层，外加两侧没有建筑物可以折射、衍射，可能用不了这款网桥。（暂未测试）</p>\n<p>是否还有其他解决方案？</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.v2ex.co/m4K924XC.jpeg\"/></p>\n", "last_modified": 1611375636, "replies": 44, "id": 747638}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_large.png?m=1604596644", "name": "bb", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_normal.png?m=1604596644", "title": "宽带症候群", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb", "topics": 8943, "footer": "", "header": "网速很重要。比快更快。", "title_alternative": "Broadband Symptom Complex", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1604596644", "stars": 4780, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 108, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"username": "leinard", "website": null, "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0c7b1f439fa3544c190cb0cf141d8ad9?s=24&d=retro", "bio": null, "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/leinard", "tagline": null, "twitter": null, "created": 1608563018, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0c7b1f439fa3544c190cb0cf141d8ad9?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0c7b1f439fa3544c190cb0cf141d8ad9?s=24&d=retro", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 524963}, "last_reply_by": "zx4824", "last_touched": 1611402163, "title": 